## Instructions

Please initialize the GBA project by completing the following steps:

### Step 1: Create Directory Structure

Create the following directory structure:

```
.gba/
├── config.yml
├── features/
│   └── .gitkeep
├── templates/
│   └── .gitkeep
.trees/
└── .gitkeep
```

Execute these commands:
```bash
mkdir -p .gba/features
mkdir -p .gba/templates
mkdir -p .trees
touch .gba/features/.gitkeep
touch .gba/templates/.gitkeep
touch .trees/.gitkeep
```

### Step 2: Update .gitignore

Update the `.gitignore` file in the repository root to exclude feature state files while keeping the directory structure:

```
# GBA feature state files (do not commit)
.gba/features/*/state.yml

# But keep the directories
!.gba/features/
!.gba/features/.gitkeep
!.gba/templates/
!.gba/templates/.gitkeep
```

### Step 3: Create config.yml

Create `.gba/config.yml` with the following structure. Replace `<project-name>`, `<user>`, and `<repo>` with appropriate values detected from the repository. Set `main_branch` to the detected main branch.

```yaml
# GBA Project Configuration
version: "1.0"

# Project metadata
project:
  name: "<project-name>"
  repository:
    url: "https://github.com/<user>/<repo>.git"
    mainBranch: "{{ main_branch }}"

# Agent defaults
agent:
  model: "claude-sonnet-4-20250514"
  maxTokens: 4096
  temperature: 0.7
  timeout: 300

# Prompt templates configuration
prompts:
  directory: "./.gba/templates"
  useBundled: true  # Fall back to bundled templates if not found locally

# Repository scanning settings
repository:
  excludePatterns:
    - "target/"
    - ".git/"
    - "node_modules/"
  maxFileSize: 1048576  # 1MB

# Logging configuration
logging:
  level: "info"
  format: "human"

# Worktree configuration
worktree:
  directory: "./.trees"
  branchPrefix: "gba/"

# Execution limits
limits:
  maxTurns: 100
  maxCostUsd: 10.0
```
